{"tid":632473,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"細妹同女朋友好似唔係好啱","createTime":"2018-04-17T11:55:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T13:01:28.000Z","uid":1369,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5c243e9d28395ae4240a6a4d2f1359b1ef7f930d","tid":632473,"uid":1369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T11:55:52.000Z","msg":"小弟23歲 細妹細我6年<br />\n<br />\n我同我而家個女朋友一齊咗快一年了<br />\n<br />\n唔係中學嗰啲puppy love 所以近排就開始帶女朋友翻屋企食飯<br />\n<br />\n但係問題就來了 我發覺細妹知我有女朋友之後就痴我多咗。 平時知道我女朋友上黎食飯次次都黑口黑面<br />\n<br />\n就係上個星期我約咗條女去海狗公園玩 <br />\n佢知道之後即刻換衫話要跟埋去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又要坐副駕位 明明平時都坐開後座 <br />\n食飯又話食唔曬 要同我share一個餐 <br />\n<br />\n到玩機動遊戲話自己一個坐會驚 死都要同我坐 咁我咪話 「不如你同姐姐坐好冇？」<br />\n佢又死都唔肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然女朋友好似冇乜嘢咁 但我都知佢實有唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可以點解決？"},{"pid":"833a975e81d3868c7ed18bd00e7236a5bf3f0fcd","tid":632473,"uid":1369,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T11:56:58.000Z","msg":"兩個我都好錫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e74ae00ec08c973773baf051f5d876376a9ff5ab","tid":632473,"uid":92603,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T11:57:30.000Z","msg":"相處耐d應該就冇問題"},{"pid":"6639d004d954abd0becb47c5728ac6ec30036312","tid":632473,"uid":173191,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"833a975e81d3868c7ed18bd00e7236a5bf3f0fcd","tid":632473,"uid":1369,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T11:56:58.000Z","msg":"兩個我都好錫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T11:57:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">A09!!!!!!!!</span></span>"},{"pid":"51fd3f51e2b7cbf292b0e463f87eb85cc71a8ac6","tid":632473,"uid":181063,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{